# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok an explosion and fire rocked an insulation factory in southern kentucky on thursday morning , injuring ## workers , at least ## of them critically .
# ::alignments
(r / rock-01
      :ARG0 (a / and
            :op1 (e / explode-01)
            :op2 (f / fire))
      :ARG1 (f2 / factory
            :mod (ii / insulate-01)
            :location (s / south
                  :part-of (s2 / state
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Kentucky"))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)
            :dayperiod (m / morning))
      :ARG0-of (ii2 / injure-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (w / work-01))
                  :op2 (p2 / person
                        :ARG1-of (ii3 / include-91
                              :ARG2 (p3 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (w2 / work-01))
                              :ARG3 (a3 / at-least
                                    :op1 (p4 / person
                                          :ARG1-of (c / critical-03))))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok colin montgomerie promises it will be different this time , even if the outcome is still the same .
# ::alignments
(p / promise-01
      :ARG0 (p2 / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Colin"
                  :op2 "Montgomerie"))
      :ARG2 (d / differ-02
            :ARG1 (ii / it)
            :time (t / this)
            :concession (e / even-if
                  :op1 (s / same-01
                        :ARG1 (o / outcome)
                        :mod (s2 / still)))))

                  :mod (g2 / great)

                  :ARG1-of (p4 / possible-01))))
